#. FzHMk
#: layer_tipps.xhp
msgctxt ""
"layer_tipps.xhp\n"
"par_id3149883\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You cannot edit objects on a locked layer."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂວັດຖຸທີ່ຢູ່ໃນຊັ້ນທີ່ຖືກລັອກໄວ້ໄດ້."

