#. GSWgX
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3149262\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can rotate an object around its default pivot point (center point) or a pivot point that you designate."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດໝູນວັດຖຸອ້ອມຈຸດໝູນມາດຕະຖານ (ຈຸດສູນກາງ) ຫຼື ຈຸດໝູນທີ່ທ່ານກຳນົດເອງໄດ້."

#. ZGoP9
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3146975\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id3154729\" src=\"cmd/sc_toggleobjectrotatemode.png\" width=\"0.564cm\" height=\"0.564cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3154729\">Icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id3154729\" src=\"cmd/sc_toggleobjectrotatemode.png\" width=\"0.564cm\" height=\"0.564cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3154729\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>"

#. GoxPE
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3150716\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the object you want to rotate. On the <emph>Transformations</emph> toolbar in $[officename] Draw or on the <emph>Drawing</emph> bar in $[officename] Impress, click the <emph>Rotate</emph> icon."
msgstr "ເລືອກວັດຖຸທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໝູນ. ໃນແຖບເຄື່ອງມື <emph>ການແປງຮູບ</emph> ໃນ $[officename] Draw ຫຼື ໃນແຖບ <emph>ການແຕ້ມ</emph> ໃນ $[officename] Impress, ໃຫ້ຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນ <emph>ໝູນ</emph>."

#. MLBay
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3149021\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Move the pointer to a corner handle so that the pointer changes to a rotate symbol. Drag the handle to rotate the object."
msgstr "ຍ້າຍຕົວຊີ້ໄປທີ່ມຸມຈົນກວ່າຕົວຊີ້ຈະປ່ຽນເປັນສັນຍະລັກການໝູນ. ລາກມຸມນັ້ນເພື່ອໝູນວັດຖຸ."

#. TrVS9
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id0930200803002335\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Hold down the Shift key to restrict the rotation to multiples of 15 degrees."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ Shift ຄ້າງໄວ້ເພື່ອຈຳກັດການໝູນໃຫ້ເປັນເທື່ອລະ 15 ອົງສາ."

#. 7nDAL
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id0930200803002463\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right-click the object to open the context menu. Choose <menuitem>Position and Size - Rotation</menuitem> to enter an exact rotation value."
msgstr "ຄລິກຂວາທີ່ວັດຖຸເພື່ອເປີດເມນູ. ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຕຳແໜ່ງ ແລະ ຂະໜາດ - ການໝູນ</menuitem> ເພື່ອປ້ອນຄ່າອົງສາການໝູນທີ່ແນ່ນອນ."

#. G5NAB
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3155962\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image id=\"img_id3154023\" src=\"media/helpimg/rotieren.png\" width=\"5.424cm\" height=\"3.916cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3154023\">Icon</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image id=\"img_id3154023\" src=\"media/helpimg/rotieren.png\" width=\"5.424cm\" height=\"3.916cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id3154023\">ໄອຄອນ</alt></image>"

#. FrzvS
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3166424\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To change the pivot point, drag the small circle in the center of the object to a new location."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ່ຽນຈຸດໝູນ, ໃຫ້ລາກວົງມົນນ້ອຍໆທີ່ຢູ່ກາງວັດຖຸໄປໄວ້ຕຳແໜ່ງໃໝ່."

#. 7Sjf8
#: rotate_object.xhp
msgctxt ""
"rotate_object.xhp\n"
"par_id3159236\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To skew the object vertically or horizontally, drag one of the side handles."
msgstr "ເພື່ອບິດວັດຖຸທາງຕັ້ງ ຫຼື ທາງນອນ, ໃຫ້ລາກຈຸດຈັບທີ່ຢູ່ດ້ານຂ້າງ."

